{"tid":1845852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】陳健波所屬集團捐1000萬抗疫　支援香港、湖北省各半","createTime":"2020-01-27T11:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T12:41:32.000Z","uid":85180,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cdeccbcee403cec1af05364c1b3d13cdffb82925","tid":1845852,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】陳健波所屬集團捐1000萬抗疫 支援香港、湖北省各半<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3919995/org/77f4c11ff89a4f21e6a6533207313a96.jpg/BQDL9Stn79WZKu3CpEtkcFOVsVjpWedlHJecsRyXnLE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3919995%2Forg%2F77f4c11ff89a4f21e6a6533207313a96.jpg%2FBQDL9Stn79WZKu3CpEtkcFOVsVjpWedlHJecsRyXnLE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=22c83f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情持續擴散，立橋保險集團行政總裁、立法會議員陳健波今（27日）宣布，為支援香港及湖北省對抗疫情，立橋保險集團將捐出港幣1,000萬元，其中500萬給予香港志願機構在港進行民間抗疫工作，另外500萬則給予湖北省，以支援當地的抗疫工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3919820/org/6042e7c26961966d8562035f93c5e83c.jpg/PQQu_h_XvDwrbxdasj4hFR0qnqxJ1DZhQVMt9UFTLfU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3919820%2Forg%2F6042e7c26961966d8562035f93c5e83c.jpg%2FPQQu_h_XvDwrbxdasj4hFR0qnqxJ1DZhQVMt9UFTLfU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e23643ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳健波表示，希望香港政府能夠推出有效措施，包括確保口罩供應正常，不會出現炒賣的情況。（資料圖片/盧翊銘攝）<br />\n<br />\n促港府三招穩民心<br />\n<br />\n陳健波表示，希望香港政府能夠推出有效措施，讓香港市民能安心，包括：<br />\n<br />\n1.確保口罩供應正常，不會出現炒賣及抬價；<br />\n<br />\n2.確保公營醫療體系足夠的人手、裝備及設施處理疫情，視乎情況給予有關醫護人員合適的特別津貼；<br />\n<br />\n3.加強各出入口的管制、檢疫、申報及隔離措施，及時控制疫情避免擴散。<br />\n<br />\n澄清非一刀切反對封關<br />\n<br />\n陳健波早前在電台節目稱，中港兩地交流頻密，「大家都係一家人」，不可輕易「封關」，其後被部分人批評反對封關，他今日接受記者訪問時強調，他並非一刀切反對封關，而是要視乎實際情況，而當日他在電台所說的意思是，中港交流頻繁，中國幅員廣闊，香港許多日常生活必需品都來自內地， 所以不能隨便封關，但當時他亦指出如果疫情「真係好緊要」，死亡率又高， 港府便應再作考慮，「所以重點是不能隨便或者係輕率決定 封關，假如疫情嚴重惡化，封關的好處比壞處多，相信政府會作出適當的行動」。"},{"pid":"d52902e4bd04d82f36dbf786ffc875a809a15fb0","tid":1845852,"uid":128328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:19:36.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"c237690eb6f05f4f322856e54ae9bb4c937cca86","tid":1845852,"uid":101307,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:21:13.000Z","msg":"你捐你事 唔好拎我地啲錢"},{"pid":"677c3d018115ed2ecbb091ed98c2f625761d56d6","tid":1845852,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:22:02.000Z","msg":"湖北政府又有額外收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56505ac540921327b5f78ac6e10b2625e347074","tid":1845852,"uid":218731,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:22:14.000Z","msg":"親自上去湖北派啦 過幾手得返幾千蚊淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34dedc72d33d6f3f94e71f976afd06c624ccad3c","tid":1845852,"uid":311309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:22:22.000Z","msg":"你捐撚哂到好 咪撚用香港人啲錢就得"},{"pid":"61678305cf6ec2b03aca6806cf775537bfe8150f","tid":1845852,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatfat"},{"pid":"eaa75ea1a11a2dd78a03c5cc59151153984696a0","tid":1845852,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:30:23.000Z","msg":"又貪污<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a43d055693e68d5993cb227868c944bec84bab","tid":1845852,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:31:04.000Z","msg":"又為奶，班官都係"},{"pid":"15a54507baf7f66b6d0fea45ba97ddd7588e00b6","tid":1845852,"uid":215249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:43:32.000Z","msg":"呢一千萬有幾多本身係我地？"},{"pid":"dd5bdf4b571467baecc2e7475776e76f1479b482","tid":1845852,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:46: